{"tid":791430,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚反骨b 😡伊禾比:「艾馬利好過雲爺爺！」","createTime":"2018-08-23T19:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T12:42:15.000Z","uid":34899,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9d9849d7168f8a98406fe9f5fefba4aa03ce5512","tid":791430,"uid":34899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:07:52.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴中場伊禾比在接受傳媒訪問時稱，他在艾馬利麾下獲得的進步，比在雲格帶隊的時候更多。<br />\n<br />\n這名22歲尼日利亞球員稱：「艾馬利令我獲益良多，令我變得更強，更能表現自己。不單單是我，還是對整支球隊都有幫助。我們都很喜歡他的訓練，他有很多新的構思，在有球無球時，我們都有所得著。作為一位進攻球員，我很喜歡在他帶領下拿到皮球。我當然想雲格留下，但艾馬利的確比雲格好，他能令我們變得更好。」<br />\n<br />\n這名尼日利亞國腳是阿仙奴的青訓產品，由雲格親手提拔上一隊，由2015年至今為兵工廠上陣99次，攻入10球。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180824/58600040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180824%2F58600040&d=Y6b7QeYkFTja28voM7JRQNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f273fc17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180824%2F58600040&h=b3f1c759\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180824/58600040</a>"},{"pid":"7dcc4b84d32f4c99b3fd09a8e8e838228db0f4c5","tid":791430,"uid":34899,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:08:27.000Z","msg":"冇爺爺 您條垃圾踢英冠炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac0185916b6fb7eb9d51a283f65d96da4bd7685","tid":791430,"uid":5549,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:20:01.000Z","msg":"事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513d11f07f5f4449f9d7076e00ef06237ffede8f","tid":791430,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:22:00.000Z","msg":"259"},{"pid":"dfb7d82ab841fdf13b54a933af9413f0c71241e9","tid":791430,"uid":31744,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:22:48.000Z","msg":"係兒登班